ate a system\nlibrary for programmers to invoke FindeR to perform EPMs in genome analysis.\nCompared to state-of-the-art accelerators, FindeR improves the FM-Index search\nthroughput by $83\\%\\sim 30K\\times$ and throughput per Watt by $3.5\\times\\sim\n42.5K\\times$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 00:50:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2019 19:18:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-03"}
