acterize local systems outside\nthe cohomology support loci of $f$ near $\\mathfrak{x}$ in terms of the\nsimplicity of modules derived from $F^{S}.$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 15:22:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jul 2019 08:20:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2019 16:42:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 28 May 2020 17:19:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-29"}
