{3/2}$) hidden-charm pentaquark is ever observed, this will in\nturn imply a second multiplet structure resembling the light-baryon decuplet:\n$P_{Q' \\bar{Q}}^{\\Delta}$, $P_{Q' \\bar{Q}}^{\\Sigma^*}$, $P_{Q'\n\\bar{Q}}^{\\Xi^*}$, $P_{Q' \\bar{Q}}^{\\Omega}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 15:48:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 17:28:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
